22:21.078 --> 22:22.079
Lila...

22:23.690 --> 22:25.779
I know you're upset,

22:25.822 --> 22:28.216
but Jenna made her decision.

22:28.259 --> 22:30.653
Just respect it, okay?

22:30.697 --> 22:34.265
My God, you--you're young.

22:34.309 --> 22:36.050
