22:54.808 --> 22:57.114
- So what'll it take
to make you go away?

22:58.812 --> 23:01.858
Come on, Ricky.
Give me a number.

23:04.861 --> 23:07.864
Wow.
You want to buy me.

23:11.128 --> 23:12.260
$10 million.

23:12.303 --> 23:14.567
Wow.
You're pathetic.

23:14.610 --> 23:17.221
- But I'm getting closer,
aren't I?

23:17.265 --> 23:19.920
$20 million.

23:22.966 --> 23:24.925
♪

23:24.968 --> 23:26.970
- I'm not for sale.

23:29.712 --> 23:31.975
I built this life from nothing.

23:32.019 --> 23:33.542
I can do it again.

23:35.065 --> 23:36.676
That's right.

23:36.719 --> 23:39.418
Hardscrabble Rick
with his bootstrap stories.

23:39.461 --> 23:40.810
But at the end of the day,

23:40.854 --> 23:42.508
too chickenshit
to pull the trigger.

23:42.551 --> 23:45.119
- God, you know, the fact that
you think that's a weakness

23:45.162 --> 23:47.513
