23:47.556 --> 23:51.342
- My father always knew
you'd never be one of us.

23:51.386 --> 23:55.477
He used to joke
that you reeked of trash.

23:55.521 --> 23:59.350
Poor white trash.

23:59.394 --> 24:01.352
- Fuck you.

24:03.311 --> 24:05.574
Aw, I know that look.

24:05.618 --> 24:08.708
Same one you gave me
on the first night.

24:08.751 --> 24:12.102
Now, do you need me to go
fuck your wife again for you?

24:19.588 --> 24:26.595
♪

24:43.394 --> 24:44.787
- Nice to see you.

24:44.831 --> 24:47.790
[elegant classical music
playing]

24:47.834 --> 24:53.274
♪

24:53.317 --> 24:54.493
Honey.

24:58.018 --> 24:59.759
- Oh, so beautiful.

25:01.412 --> 25:03.545
- Big day, Lila.

25:03.589 --> 25:05.634
- Good luck.

25:05.678 --> 25:07.897
- If I could just,
for a second,

25:07.941 --> 25:09.682
have your attention.

25:09.725 --> 25:12.511
- Hi!

25:12.554 --> 25:15.209
- I'd like to thank you all
for coming,

25:15.252 --> 25:18.038
for celebrating
this occasion with us

25:18.081 --> 25:19.126
in our home...

25:21.128 --> 25:22.346
And with our daughter,

25:22.390 --> 25:24.392
our spectacular Lila.

25:24.435 --> 25:25.393
Look at you.
You're just--

25:27.613 --> 25:29.353
- You're stunning.

25:29.397 --> 25:30.703
Your mother and I
have always known

25:30.746 --> 25:32.269
that you were destined
for magnificence.

25:32.313 --> 25:34.837
And we--we truly could not
be prouder of you.

25:35.795 --> 25:39.581
Tonight is momentous.

25:39.625 --> 25:41.757
But it's just
the first commencement.

25:41.801 --> 25:44.934
To a lifetime
of glorious participation.

25:44.978 --> 25:47.284
- Yeah. Cheers.
all: Cheers.

25:47.328 --> 25:48.416
- Hear, hear.
- To Lila.

25:48.459 --> 25:50.984
- Cheers, Lila.
- Mm-hmm.

25:51.027 --> 25:54.944
- And now our gift on the eve
of your 18th birthday.

25:54.988 --> 25:56.467
Gentlemen?

26:01.168 --> 26:08.175
♪

26:23.930 --> 26:30.197
♪

26:30.240 --> 26:32.068
- Ah, it's a big decision.

26:32.112 --> 26:34.375
- Choose your path.

26:34.418 --> 26:36.116
Whenever you're ready, love.

26:40.555 --> 26:43.776
♪

26:43.819 --> 26:45.821
- Shh, shh, she needs
to concentrate.

26:45.865 --> 26:50.652
♪

26:50.696 --> 26:52.741
- Oh-ho-ho.
- Oh, great choice.

26:52.785 --> 26:54.569
- Wonderful.

26:54.613 --> 26:56.484
- That's my girl.

26:56.527 --> 27:03.534
♪

27:19.942 --> 27:21.640
A toast to my daughter.

27:21.683 --> 27:23.206
all: Cheers.

27:23.250 --> 27:25.469
- We're all here
to celebrate her

27:25.513 --> 27:28.603
and to support her
on her journey.

27:28.647 --> 27:30.083
To Lila.

27:30.126 --> 27:32.694
all: To Lila.

