28:55.037 --> 28:57.692
Purging?

28:57.736 --> 29:01.000
- It's a little personal
tonight.

29:01.043 --> 29:02.653
I'm doing my own thing.

29:04.220 --> 29:05.831
- Yeah.

29:05.874 --> 29:07.615
Had to find someone tonight.

29:07.658 --> 29:09.312
That's why I'm out here.

29:09.356 --> 29:11.532
Had to bring her
somewhere safe.

29:17.625 --> 29:19.192
- Yeah, you know,
this holiday

29:19.235 --> 29:21.847
feels like it lasts
a whole lifetime

29:21.890 --> 29:24.545
when you're in it,
but then the sun comes up.

29:27.983 --> 29:30.203
- I think, first things first,
I'm gonna get breakfast.

29:30.246 --> 29:32.553
- Ah.

29:32.596 --> 29:34.947
- Yeah, tomorrow can't come
fast enough, you know?

29:36.818 --> 29:38.124
- Huh.

29:39.429 --> 29:41.431
First day
of the rest of my life.

29:43.607 --> 29:44.826
I'm Joe.

29:44.870 --> 29:47.002
- Miguel.

29:47.046 --> 29:49.570
- Cheers, Miguel.
- Cheers.

29:49.613 --> 29:51.398
- Thank you for your service.

29:54.444 --> 30:01.451
♪

30:06.717 --> 30:09.677
