indistinct speech]

30:09.720 --> 30:16.727
♪

30:35.659 --> 30:42.666
♪

30:53.721 --> 31:00.728
♪

31:15.482 --> 31:17.614
- That bus is full of kids
just like me--

31:17.658 --> 31:19.703
lost and so sure they're doing
the right thing.

31:19.747 --> 31:22.184
They deserve to know
the truth about Tavis.

31:22.228 --> 31:24.056
- Would they even
believe you?

31:24.099 --> 31:27.189
- I mean, they know me.
Maybe they'd believe me.

31:27.233 --> 31:30.018
- Pen, even if you could
convince any of them--

31:30.062 --> 31:32.194
any of them--we almost died
getting back here.

31:32.238 --> 31:33.935
More than once.

31:33.979 --> 31:35.415
- I know that,
but they're all gonna die,

31:35.458 --> 31:37.156
and it's my fault
they're out there.

31:37.199 --> 31:39.549
- They're not our problem.
