31:51.213 --> 31:52.171
- Pete, gun!
- Miguel!

31:54.347 --> 31:56.392
- Rocco, move your ass!

31:58.917 --> 32:04.052
♪

32:06.446 --> 32:09.710
You motherfucker, Pete!

32:09.753 --> 32:12.452
My brother's rotting in prison
'cause of you!

32:14.410 --> 32:16.717
- Hey, Samuel, it's Penelope.

32:16.760 --> 32:18.545
I need to talk to Tavis.

32:20.199 --> 32:22.244
- Rossito. Zeke Rossito.

32:22.288 --> 32:25.160
Brian's brother?

32:25.204 --> 32:28.120
That sick bastard deserves
to be behind bars for life.

32:28.163 --> 32:29.686
Get him out of here!

32:29.730 --> 32:31.601
- Come on, you shit bag.
Get him up, Rocco.

32:31.645 --> 32:33.647
Get him. Get him.
- Take him outside!

32:35.605 --> 32:37.868
- Move, move, move!
- Get out of here.

32:37.912 --> 32:41.481
- Anybody else want to ruin
a good thing tonight?

32:46.094 --> 32:47.878
- Good luck out there.

32:58.802 --> 33:01.022
- Pete.

33:01.066 --> 33:04.373
Hey, listen, Penelope told me
something about--

33:04.417 --> 33:06.941
Where's Penelope?
- Shit.

33:06.985 --> 33:09.378
Probably shouldn't have
told her about Tavis.

33:09.422 --> 33:11.815
- Wait, you don't think
she really--

33:11.859 --> 33:14.775
- Check the bathrooms.
I got the office.

33:45.371 --> 33:52.334
♪

33:52.378 --> 33:53.944
- Aah!
- Oh!

33:53.988 --> 33:57.165
- Aah! Aah! Aah!

34:00.038 --> 34:01.343
You did this.

34:01.387 --> 34:03.084
You chose this.
- Lila, stop!

34:03.128 --> 34:04.564
- Jenna, Jenna, Jenna,
go back upstairs.

34:04.607 --> 34:06.044
- It's okay.
I'm protecting us.

34:06.087 --> 34:07.610
He grabbed me.
He tried to kill me.

34:07.654 --> 34:08.742
- No, I don't want
any more violence tonight.

34:08.785 --> 34:10.352
- He's a violent man!

34:10.396 --> 34:13.703
What if he hurts you
or the

34:13.747 --> 34:15.227
Would you risk that?
Would you raise our child

34:15.270 --> 34:16.663
with this monster?

34:16.706 --> 34:18.882
- She's not your child.
- Rick, no!

34:18.926 --> 34:20.580
No.
- I was there when it happened.

34:20.623 --> 34:23.278
You needed me
to make her happen.

34:23.322 --> 34:26.020
But now you want to cut me
out of your life?

34:26.064 --> 34:27.761
He's making you do this.
I know he is.

34:27.804 --> 34:29.067
He hates what we have.

34:29.110 --> 34:30.198
- Put the gun down.

34:30.242 --> 34:32.548
Put it down.

34:37.249 --> 34:38.989
Tell me I'm not crazy.

34:39.033 --> 34:41.035
Because I don't know
what's real anymore.

34:41.079 --> 34:43.124
- Yes. It was real.

34:43.168 --> 34:44.734
It was real
when I said those things.

34:44.778 --> 34:46.780
I meant them when I said them.

34:46.823 --> 34:49.174
I'm so sorry I hurt you.

34:49.217 --> 34:52.220
Okay?
Please, I'm sorry.

34:52.264 --> 34:53.221
Please.

34:53.265 --> 34:55.093
- I know you love me.

34:56.572 --> 34:58.052
You'll understand one day,
I did this for us.

34:58.096 --> 34:59.053
- No, no, no!

35:11.761 --> 35:18.768
♪

35:41.356 --> 35:46.883
♪

36:02.290 --> 36:09.297
♪

36:22.441 --> 36:25.139
♪

36:25.183 --> 36:29.274
- Get back here, you traitor!

36:29.317 --> 36:31.014
- Come here, you bitch!

36:39.109 --> 36:46.073
♪

36:52.645 --> 36:53.863
- Tavis.

36:53.907 --> 36:57.302
I need to talk to you.

36:57.345 --> 36:59.956
- Sister Penny,
you're alive.

37:00.000 --> 37:02.829
We came as fast
as we could.

37:02.872 --> 37:04.265
Come.

37:04.309 --> 37:06.049
- Don't listen to anything
Tavis says.

37:06.093 --> 37:07.355
She's a liar
who wants us to die.

37:07.399 --> 37:09.009
She gets paid for it.

37:09.052 --> 37:10.924
- Sister Penelope, please.
- Stay away from me!

37:10.967 --> 37:14.406
Listen, get off the bus now
and come inside, please.

37:14.449 --> 37:16.321
We'll be safe.
- You've gotten lost

37:16.364 --> 37:18.497
on your way to the Invisible.

37:18.540 --> 37:19.846
You're not the first.

37:19.889 --> 37:22.240
- I saw the night
for what it really is.

37:22.283 --> 37:24.807
- A chance for us to heal
those who are suffering and--

37:24.851 --> 37:27.201
- No, your chance
to line your pockets.

37:27.245 --> 37:28.681
You never told us
that you were funded

37:28.724 --> 37:30.813
by the New Founding Fathers.

37:30.857 --> 37:33.903
- The people I care for
have no means.

37:33.947 --> 37:37.037
All of the money is used
to support the mission,

37:37.080 --> 37:39.953
to support people like you,
like all of you.

37:39.996 --> 37:41.215
- Look, don't let her
twist this.

37:41.259 --> 37:42.912
She picked us
because the NFFA

37:42.956 --> 37:44.305
told her we were disposable.

37:44.349 --> 37:46.960
- I didn't choose you.
You chose me.

37:47.003 --> 37:49.789
I am trying to make the world
a better place

37:49.832 --> 37:52.357
by any means necessary.
- Bullshit.

37:52.400 --> 37:55.142
- You understood that once.

37:55.185 --> 37:58.406
Were you not happy
under my care?

37:58.450 --> 38:00.147
- I was, but it was based--

38:00.190 --> 38:02.410
- You were.

38:02.454 --> 38:05.500
You were happy.

38:05.544 --> 38:07.894
And now self-interest
has clouded your judgment

38:07.937 --> 38:09.678
and made you weak.

38:11.767 --> 38:14.683
I should've known
that you weren't ready.

38:14.727 --> 38:17.556
Not yet.
Not this year.

38:22.735 --> 38:24.345
- Not ever.

38:25.955 --> 38:27.217
- What the hell do you think
you're doing? Come here!

38:27.261 --> 38:28.480
Let go of me!

38:28.523 --> 38:30.830
- Let her go.

38:30.873 --> 38:32.614
- Hey, man,
I just drive the bus.

38:37.619 --> 38:39.055
- I don't want to die.

38:39.099 --> 38:40.796
- How about I take you
somewhere safe?

38:40.840 --> 38:42.363
- The Cantina. It's safe.

38:42.407 --> 38:44.496
- No.

38:44.539 --> 38:46.367
Miguel!

38:49.414 --> 38:53.243
♪

38:53.287 --> 38:55.507
- Pen!

38:56.986 --> 38:58.031
Pen!

38:58.074 --> 39:01.164
♪

39:01.208 --> 39:02.818
Penelope!

39:04.559 --> 39:07.083
Pen! Pen!

39:07.127 --> 39:13.046
♪

39:17.050 --> 39:18.921
- I did this.

39:21.968 --> 39:24.187
- You saved my life.

39:26.451 --> 39:28.844
Hey.

39:28.888 --> 39:32.195
Hey.

39:32.239 --> 39:34.241
We're gonna be okay.

39:35.721 --> 39:36.896
I promise.

39:36.939 --> 39:38.463
- System disarmed.

39:42.162 --> 39:44.469
